    • produceBoxedMilk

      public void produceBoxedMilk​(Milk milk) throws ItemNotCountableException
      Factory makes the production so, that's why we have this method in here. As in a real factory, every product has its own production method in this class. This is the one for the boxed milk products. It produces 1000L boxed milk for 1000L milk.
      Parameters:
      milk - Given raw material milk.
      Throws:
      ItemNotCountableException - If you try to put an "uncountable" item into a wrong place, you get this exception.

      Factory makes the production so, that's why we have this method in here. As in a real factory, every product has its own production method in this class. This is the one for the chocolate products. It produces 800L chocolate for 500L milk, 200L cream and 300L cacao.
